review.description: I've been to this location on several occasions and enjoy the wings depending on who takes my order. There is a young woman who works the register who rushes you and ignores any special request on your order- I mean literally pretends she doesn't hear you - other than her I think this is cool late nightspot to grab some quick grub
review.author: Mr. T.

review.description: WING STOP BROOKLYN STOP IT!!!! HORRIBLE they lost so many orders tonight, it was crazy.  There was a lady there behind the counter with no uniform (maybe the owner) and her long hair flowing without a hat.  I tried to call my order in and as usual they DON'T ANSWER THE PHONE! I came in ordered 55 wings and it took an HOUR! WOW! WING STOP WAS ONE OF MY FAVORITE PLACES, AS A TEXAN, I WAS SO HAPPY TO KNOW THEY WERE COMING TO BROOKLYN...... MAN I WILL DO LIKE I HAVE BEEN DOING AND WAIT TILL I GO HOME! ewwww! service sad and the lack of training shows. AND MY ORDER WASN'T RIGHT...I JUST SAID FORGET IT!
review.author: Nichelle M.

review.description: ate here for the first time- hadn't seen a Wing Stop since texas! and it is just how i remember- BBq goodness that doesn't taste like fast food
review.author: Lori Z.
